cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.CR, cs.AI, cs.NE 

This paper proposes a defense against adversarial attacks on deep neural networks for image classification problems. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves deep neural networks, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper deals with security and adversarial attacks, which could place it in cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). Additionally, the paper involves the use of simple image transformations, which could suggest it belongs to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) or cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
